<title role="details.title">Details</title>
<refsect2 id="GtkClutterZoomable-struct" role="struct">
<title>GtkClutterZoomable</title>
<indexterm zone="GtkClutterZoomable-struct"><primary>GtkClutterZoomable</primary></indexterm><programlisting>typedef struct _GtkClutterZoomable GtkClutterZoomable;</programlisting>
<para>
</para></refsect2>
